Chess clock for Arduino Uno ...
work in progess :)

Currently Fischer 5 seconds is supported. 

CHANGE LOG


1. May 2014
Corrected time interval. It is 1 sec now.

28. April 2014
Early alpha of chess clock - some rough edges and not sure if clocks follow the logic of "proper" clocks.
Discussion needed.

21. April 2014
Added menu to select clock type and reading of the other keys (up, down, select)

